---
title: Hoisin Turkey Tacos with Tangy-Sweet Cilantro Slaw & Lime Mayo
description: The versatile taco is taking a trip to southeast Asia with these sweet, savory, and spicy handheld bites. Tender ground turkey cooks along with hoisin sauce, pho stock, lime juice, and as much Sriracha as you like. We pile the flavorful filling into warm flour tortillas and top them with a crisp and tangy cilantro slaw, balancing the rich filling.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/670d6245dc533226ca913a68-7beaf41e.jpeg
